        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We find ourselves making a stir fry in the candle lit load shedding quite perturbed by how normal the whole situation is. We know deep down that this is just a a layover of sorts. But it’s been a necessary rest. The bags are packed and we’re excited. ",
            "link": null
          },
